data.description: GREAT location for a small hobby farm and/or winter rental.  Just add some fencing and a run in shed and you're ready to go!!  This quaint little well priced home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with an open concept and 2 living areas.  Located within minutes of the Windsor Trace Driving Community and only a short 25 minute drive to Hitchcock Woods 2000 acres of trails.  With some TLC, you can certainly make this place your own.  All appliances will convey as well as the 2018 Husqvarna 54'' mower.  What are you waiting for??!
